* :XYZk0RcElkiIMFNY: multiple Dockerfiles sharing a context
    @created 1493933749587
    @weight 0.5

Specify the Dockerfile separately from, and in a subfolder of, the context:

  docker build -f docker-files/Dockerfile .

Source: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/27068596/how-to-include-files-outside-of-dockers-build-context